  "title": "Service Crew | From $2,600 + Incentives | Multiple Outlets",
  "description": "<h3>Working Hours</h3><ul><li><p>Shift-based (retail / F&B operating hours)</p></li><li><p>6-day work week</p></li><li><p>1 rest day per week (rostered)</p></li></ul><h3>Job Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Provide friendly and professional customer service</p></li><li><p>Take customer orders and handle POS transactions</p></li><li><p>Serve food and beverages accurately and promptly</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of service areas</p></li><li><p>Support daily outlet operations and teamwork</p></li></ul><h3>Job Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Prior F&B or customer service experience preferred (training provided)</p></li><li><p>Able to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays</p></li><li><p>Service-oriented with positive attitude</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working in a fast-paced environment</p></li><li><p>Willing to commit to full-time employment</p></li></ul><h3>Additional Information</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Mass hiring for new and upcoming outlets</strong></p></li><li><p>Suitable for candidates seeking <strong>stable income and career growth</strong> in F&B</p></li></ul><p><strong>EA Licence No:</strong> 23C1703<br /><strong>EA Personnel No:</strong> R1762582<br /><strong>EA Personnel Name:</strong> Wong Choo Sian, Jabez</p>",
